            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A janni can remain on an Elemental Plane for 48 hours. Each hour it remains on such a plane thereafter, it takes 1 damage that can\u2019t be reduced in any way until it returns to the Material Plane. This endurance resets after the janni remains on the Material Plane for 24 hours.",
